sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client (Svelte)
    participant A as App (Wails Binding)
    participant PM as PlanningManager
    participant RE as RuleEngine
    participant PA as PlanAccess
    participant R as Repository (Git)

    Note over C,R: GetTasks
    C->>A: GetTasks()
    A->>PM: GetTasks()
    PM->>PA: GetBoardConfiguration()
    PA->>PA: ReadFile(board_config.json)
    PA-->>PM: *BoardConfiguration
    loop For each column + "archived"
        PM->>PA: GetTasksByStatus(status)
        PA->>PA: ReadDir(tasks/{status}/)
        PA->>PA: ReadFile each .json
        PA-->>PM: []Task
    end
    PM->>PA: LoadTaskOrder()
    PA->>PA: ReadFile(task_order.json)
    PA-->>PM: map[zone][]taskId
    PM->>PM: Sort tasks by persisted order within drop zones
    PM-->>A: []TaskWithStatus
    A->>A: Convert to Wails DTOs
    A-->>C: []TaskWithStatus (Wails DTO)

    Note over C,R: CreateTask (with rule evaluation)
    C->>A: CreateTask(title, themeId, priority, description, tags, promotionDate)
    A->>PM: CreateTask(...)
    PM->>PM: Validate priority, promotionDate format, parse tags
    PM->>PM: buildTaskInfoList()
    PM->>PM: GetTasks() [internal]
    PM->>RE: EvaluateTaskChange(EventTaskCreate)
    RE->>RE: filterApplicableRules("task_create")
    RE->>RE: checkRequiredFields(title)
    RE-->>PM: RuleEvaluationResult{Allowed: true}
    PM->>PM: Compute dropZone from todoSlug + priority
    PM->>PA: SaveTaskWithOrder(task, dropZone)
    PA->>PA: saveTaskFile() [generate ID, set timestamps]
    PA->>PA: LoadTaskOrder()
    PA->>PA: Append task to order[dropZone]
    PA->>PA: WriteJSON(task file + task_order.json)
    PA->>R: Begin() -> Stage(both files) -> Commit("Add task: X")
    PA-->>PM: *Task
    PM-->>A: *Task
    A-->>C: *Task (Wails DTO)

    Note over C,R: MoveTask (with rule evaluation)
    C->>A: MoveTask(taskId, newStatus, positions)
    A->>PM: MoveTask(taskId, newStatus, positions)
    PM->>PA: GetBoardConfiguration()
    PM->>PM: Validate newStatus against board columns
    PM->>PM: GetTasks() [find task, build context]
    PM->>RE: EvaluateTaskChange(EventTaskMove)
    RE->>RE: filterApplicableRules("task_move")
    RE->>RE: checkWIPLimit(doing column, max 20)
    RE->>RE: checkAllowedTransition(allow_all=true)
    RE->>RE: checkMaxAge(30 days)
    alt Rule violation
        RE-->>PM: {Allowed: false, Violations: [...]}
        PM-->>A: MoveTaskResult{Success: false, Violations}
        A-->>C: *MoveTaskResult
    else Rules pass
        RE-->>PM: {Allowed: true}
        PM->>PA: MoveTask(taskId, newStatus)
        PA->>PA: findTaskInPlan() [locate file]
        PA->>PA: os.Rename(old path, new path)
        PA->>R: Begin() -> Stage(old+new) -> Commit()
        PM->>PA: LoadTaskOrder()
        PM->>PM: Remove from source zone
        PM->>PM: Apply positions or append to target zone
        PM->>PA: SaveTaskOrder(orderMap)
        PA->>R: Begin() -> Stage() -> Commit()
        PM-->>A: MoveTaskResult{Success: true, Positions}
        A-->>C: *MoveTaskResult
    end

    Note over C,R: UpdateTask (with rule evaluation + zone migration)
    C->>A: UpdateTask(task)
    A->>PM: UpdateTask(access.Task)
    PM->>PM: buildTaskInfoList() [get all tasks]
    PM->>PM: Find old priority/status for zone change detection
    PM->>RE: EvaluateTaskChange(EventTaskUpdate)
    RE-->>PM: RuleEvaluationResult
    alt Priority changed & zone changed (todo task)
        PM->>PA: UpdateTaskWithOrderMove(task, oldZone, newZone)
        PA->>PA: saveTaskFile()
        PA->>PA: LoadTaskOrder() -> move ID between zones
        PA->>PA: WriteJSON(task file + task_order.json)
        PA->>R: Begin() -> Stage(both) -> Commit()
    else No zone change
        PM->>PA: SaveTask(task)
        PA->>PA: saveTaskFile()
        PA->>R: Begin() -> Stage() -> Commit()
    end
    PM-->>A: nil
    A-->>C: nil

    Note over C,R: DeleteTask
    C->>A: DeleteTask(taskId)
    A->>PM: DeleteTask(taskId)
    PM->>PA: DeleteTaskWithOrder(taskId)
    PA->>PA: findTaskInPlan()
    PA->>PA: os.Remove(task file)
    PA->>PA: LoadTaskOrder() -> remove from all zones
    PA->>PA: WriteJSON(task_order.json)
    PA->>R: Begin() -> Stage(both) -> Commit()
    PM-->>A: nil
    A-->>C: nil
